citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process between 11:25am -
12:05pm on January 27, 2023. The inspector called the licensee and waited for 30 minutes, but was unable to reach a
representative at that time.
End Section
